{"tid":1715154,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[保持警惕] 今日必定再入侵中大並且極有可能武力升級","createTime":"2019-11-13T04:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T04:38:40.000Z","uid":112814,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ac99fb6cc539e4dfbd0576fdb165ac411807275d","tid":1715154,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:30:27.000Z","msg":"撤走班ndsnds再加上直升機視察手足佈防<br />\n佢地必定計劃緊下一個進攻計劃<br />\n而撤走NDS係極有可能費事係入侵期間誤傷<br />\n而考慮到nds必然係大後方(hall) 唔係戰場<br />\n所以有理由懷疑黑狗將不擇手段 不計成本咁入侵中大並將戰線推入中大後方 否則NDS係無誤傷之危或撤走之必要<br />\n更加係怕NDS見到黑狗以致命武力屠殺中大人 同平日宣傳不符 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今日中大 明日八大 後日香港<br />\n救中大=救香港<br />\n香港人 戰鬥!!!!!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"7f2a11927e58e79509082bba09290a4b53ee9ff0","tid":1715154,"uid":337761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:30:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">連登冷氣軍師 rt like reply</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">你哋已經唔使上前線搏命，係咪連呢啲都做唔到？</span><br />\n最新<br />\n<br />\n！！！！Sen. Cory Gardner (Colorado)<br />\n關注中大 支持香港<br />\n！！！！佢未cosponsor條Act 請佢幫忙！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLafzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=14d8588e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&h=c0f128d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Sen Menendez 出聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatormenendez/status/1194349446349443072?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatormenendez%2Fstatus%2F1194349446349443072%3Fs%3D21&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLafzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=9cc71543\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed